message.content:
1. There were two groups in the study, one treated for 24 weeks and the other for 48 weeks.
2. The SVR rate in the 24-week group in the intention-to-treat analysis was 90.8%.
3. The SVR rate in the 48-week group in the intention-to-treat analysis was 88.2%.
4. The SVR rate in the 24-week group in the per-protocol analysis was 95.7%.
5. The SVR rate in the 48-week group in the per-protocol analysis was 97.0%.
6. The number of participants in the 24-week group in the intention-to-treat analysis was 76.
7. The number of participants in the 48-week group in the intention-to-treat analysis was also 76.
8. The number of participants in the 24-week group in the per-protocol analysis was 70.
9. The number of participants in the 48-week group in the per-protocol analysis was 66.
10. 69 participants in the 24-week group achieved SVR in the intention-to-treat analysis.
11. 67 participants in the 48-week group achieved SVR in the intention-to-treat analysis.
12. 67 participants in the 24-week group achieved SVR in the per-protocol analysis.
13. 64 participants in the 48-week group achieved SVR in the per-protocol analysis.

messages.content:
Statement: The SVR rates in the 24- and 48-week groups in the intention-to-treat analysis were 90.8% (69/76) and 88.2% (67/76), respectively; those in the per-protocol analysis were 95.7% (67/70) and 97.0% (64/66), respectively.
